======================
About Discussion-Forum
======================

 Discussion Forum is an application using which users can initiate a discussion or participate in an existing discussion on LAN.
 It is implemented using socket programming in C which also makes use of record locking of file and process management.

============
Installation
============

 This is pretty simple...
 - Just compile using installer file
     $ sh installer
 - To run the server
     $ ./server/server
 - To run the client program
     $ ./clent/client <server_addr> 	

=============
Demonstration
=============
 Just browse the /images directory for a small demo of various features of this application